            "id": 5907803,
            "title": "〈台股開盤〉被列關稅「骯髒」國 權值股走弱 年線保衛戰未脫險",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美股四大指數 20 日全面收黑、台灣傳出在川普政府點名的「骯髒 15 國」(the dirty 15) 之列，台股今 (21) 日以平低盤開出，開 22362.38 點，下跌 14.88 點，而在台積電走弱下，最低來到 22250.06 點，儘管聯發科、廣達權值股持穩在平盤上，但跌幅一度超過百點，年線保衛戰未脫離危險。預估全日成交量約 2100 億元，較前一日量縮。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>權值股全面走弱，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>) 下跌 1 元，跌 0.1% ；聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 持平；聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>) 跌約 1%，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>)、廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>)、日月光投控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) 均於平盤下方。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>烏克蘭 20 日襲擊俄羅斯儲油設施，停戰可能延遲，重建概念股走弱，塑化類股，台塑 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1301:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1301\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1301-TW</a>)、台化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1326:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1326\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1326-TW</a>) 跌約 2%，南亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>)、華夏 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1305:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1305\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1305-TW</a>) 跌近 2%；鋼鐵類股，大成鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2027:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2027\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2027-TW</a>)、新鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2032:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2032\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2032-TW</a>)、佳大 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2033:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2033\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2033-TW</a>) 跌約 1%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國財長貝森特（Scott Bessent）日前表示，川普政府將會如期在 4 月 2 日推出對等關稅，且會別關注對美國徵收高關稅且貿易量大國家。今日早盤 AI 類股走弱，雙鴻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3324:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3324\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3324-TW</a>)、奇鋐 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3017:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3017\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3017-TW</a>) 跌逾 1%；伺服器類股，技嘉 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2376:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2376\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2376-TW</a>) 跌逾 1%，華碩 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2357:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2357\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2357-TW</a>) 走弱。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Google 收購資安公司 Wiz，資安概念受矚目，資服股走強，華經 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2468:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2468\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2468-TW</a>) 亮紅燈，凌群 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2453:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2453\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2453-TW</a>)、零壹 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3029:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3029\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3029-TW</a>) 漲逾 3%，三商電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2427:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2427\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2427-TW</a>) 漲逾 2%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/5907803",
